---
title: Facilities
layout: "base.njk"
navActive: facilities
---

<section class="container mt-1">
  <h1>Our Facilities</h1>
  <p class="facilities-intro">We have a wide range of tools and workspaces available to our members — whether you're a seasoned craftsperson or trying something completely new. Come and see what takes your fancy.</p>

  {% if facilities.length %}
    <div class="facilities-list">
      {% for facility in facilities %}
        <article class="facility-row{% if loop.index % 2 == 0 %} facility-row--reverse{% endif %}">
          {% if facility.imageUrl %}
            <div class="facility-image">
              <img src="{{ facility.imageUrl }}?w=800&auto=format" alt="{{ facility.title }}" />
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="facility-content">
            <h2>{{ facility.title }}</h2>
            {% if facility.contentHtml %}
              {{ facility.contentHtml | safe }}
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p>No facilities listed yet — check back soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
